  "rule_text": "The masthead gradient \u2014 Sunshine \u2192 light gold (#faa31b \u2192 \u2248#ffe05c / 0C,10M,78Y,0K) \u2014 is the gradient to use with the LISRAYA logo mark for contrast, with the mark sitting at the lightest end.",
